  "texts": [
    "All images consist of single or multiply imaged parts of the straight line on the source plane.",
    "Depending on the configuration, loops can sometimes combine to form bigger loops and the main line can also be connected to stars, as can be seen on the figure.",
    "The total magnification is actually dominated by only a few images (e.g.",
    "see Rauch et al. 1992; Wambsganss 1992; Schechter and Wambsganss 2002; Granot et al. 2003; Saha and Williams 2011).",
    "This is apparent in the left panel of Fig. 4 and illustrated further in Fig."
